# 🎨 MudBlazor ThemeManager Saver v1.0.1

## 🚀 Initial Release

This is the initial release of **MudBlazor ThemeManager Saver** - an enhanced fork of the original [MudBlazor ThemeManager](https://github.com/MudBlazor/ThemeManager) with powerful theme saving and persistence capabilities!

## ✨ What's New

### 🎯 **Core Features**
- **🎨 Enhanced Theme Management**: All original ThemeManager features plus persistence
- **💾 JSON Serialization**: Save and load themes as JSON files  
- **🔄 Automatic Persistence**: Themes save automatically when modified
- **🌓 Dark/Light Mode Support**: Full palette support for both modes
- **⚡ Multi-Target Framework**: Supports .NET 8.0 and .NET 9.0

### 💾 **Persistence Options**
- **🌐 Local Storage**: Browser-based persistence for client-side apps
- **📁 File System**: Server-side file storage for Blazor Server apps  
- **📄 wwwroot JSON**: JSON files in wwwroot folder with our `ThemePersistenceService`

### 🛠️ **Technical Features**
- **🔒 Type Safety**: Strongly-typed theme models
- **🛡️ Error Handling**: Robust error handling and validation
- **🚀 Performance**: Efficient serialization and storage
- **🔧 Extensible**: Easy to add custom persistence providers

## 📦 **Components Included**

| Component | Description |
|-----------|-------------|
| `MudThemeManager` | Main theme management component |
| `MudThemeManagerButton` | Quick access button |
| `MudThemeManagerColorItem` | Individual color picker |
| `ThemePersistenceService` | Ready-to-use persistence service |

## 🚀 **Quick Start**

### 1. **Installation**
```bash
dotnet add package MudBlazor.ThemeManager.Saver